high_descs: Turn right. When you reach the wall, turn right. When you get near the fridge. Turn left. Approach the wall. Turn right and approach the fridge.
Open the egg shelf. Take the white egg. Close the egg shelf.
Turn around. Turn right at the end of the wall, turn left. Continue ahead, turn left at the second entrance. Reach the pot and turn right to the wall. Turn left, opposite the pot.
Place the egg in the pot on the right.
Grab the pot and the ball.
Leave the room. Turn right. After two entrances, turn right. Go forward to the TV. Turn left to be in front of the diningtable.
Place the pot with the ball on the left side of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Find a ball and a pot. Bring them to the round table.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take the egg from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the bedroom.
Put the egg into the pot on the bed.
Take the pot with egg from the bed.
Turn around and go to the diningtable.
Put the pot with egg on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the cooking vessel with egg in the pot on the diningtable.

high_descs: A turn around the fridge.
Open the refrigerator and take the egg.
Pot is carried nearby in bedroom.
Egg is kept in the pot.
To take the egg and pan-fry in the pot.
Egg and pan-fry is carried nearby in diningtable.

anns.task_desc: Collect the Egg and pan-fry it, then place it on the dining table.

high_descs: Walk around the counters behind you and get to the fridge.
Remove the egg from the fridge.
Turn around, go straight and turn right into the hallway, then take the last left in the hallway to approach the pot in the room.
Place the egg into the pot on the right, the pot that is closest to the head of the bed.
Pick up the pot with the egg in it.
Exit the room the way you came in, turn right and go straight down the hallway until reaching the oval white table on the right.
Place the pot down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with an egg in it on a diningtable.
